snippet.title: Gran Turismo Concept: 2002 Tokyo-Geneva - Official UK PlayStation 2 Magazine Trailer
snippet.description:
Song featured in the trailer is "Seven Days in the Sun" by Feeder, which is also featured in the PAL version of Gran Turismo 3: A-Spec.
